<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="12Feb1938"><font color="red">12 February 1938</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): Got Buddha, thanks. Also I.T. &hellip; broadcast &hellip; nothing appeared in the press &hellip; As for H.W. you had great trouble in getting me to Lausanne. I am exhausted after prodigious solitary labour &hellip; Will send you 100 frs for the typist as soon as I have it. </div>
